import { v4 as uuidv4 } from 'uuid'

export default [
  { id: uuidv4(), url: require('../../assets/img/phone2.jpg'), title: '手机' },
  { id: uuidv4(), url: require('../../assets/img/appliance5.jpg'), title: '家电' },
  { id: uuidv4(), url: require('../../assets/img/manwear4.jpg'), title: '男装' },
  { id: uuidv4(), url: require('../../assets/img/ladywear5.jpg'), title: '女装' },
  { id: uuidv4(), url: require('../../assets/img/live4.jpg'), title: '生活' },
]
